        <num>CCP 2823</num>
        <heading>2823.  Additional evidence</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2823.  Additional evidence
In any case in which evidence by affidavit is permitted under Article 2821, the court may require further evidence of any fact sworn to therein by the introduction of evidence as in ordinary cases.</p>
        </content>
